      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00048",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子下。〖吹打〗。关胜上，林冲、关胜同见，同坐。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00049",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "多劳贤弟，远路到此。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00050",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关胜"
      ],
      "text": "好说，大哥为何免战高悬？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00051",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "这丫头杀法厉害，因此免战高悬。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00052",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关胜"
      ],
      "text": "且请后面，待某会她一阵。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00053",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟须要小心。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00054",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关胜"
      ],
      "text": "不劳吩咐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00055",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关胜、林冲自两边分下。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00056",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四红旗引关胜、四下手引郑玉娥同上，同杀，过场，同下。四火旗引火星同上。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00057",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "火星"
      ],
      "text": "某，火德星君是也。今有关胜，在红桃山中有难，不免前去搭救。火卒们！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00058",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四火旗"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00059",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 59,
