      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "火星"
      ],
      "text": "起道前往。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00060",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s08",
      "scene_no": 8,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。（郑玉娥上，五色旗同上，同摆阵，众兵卒举火同上，火星上，关胜上，入阵，郑玉娥、关胜同杀，关胜闯阵，火星救关胜同下，郑玉娥、众兵卒押场同下。〖一江风〗。四喽兵引花荣同上。）",
      "text_length": 90
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00061",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "花荣"
      ],
      "text": "云雾飘飘绿水茫，青山照顶白玉霜。残秋日后飘落叶，黄花满地放清香。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00062",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花荣"
      ],
      "text": "俺，神箭手小李广花荣。奉大哥将令，前往红桃山，与林冲助阵。众好汉！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00063",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四喽兵"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00064",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "花荣"
      ],
      "text": "趱行。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02009040_e00065",
      "play_id": "02009040",
      "scene_id": "02009040_s09",
      "scene_no": 9,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
